[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_0",
    "text": "直，加固大堤：开挖入海河道(准河)：修建分洪区：建立洪水预报预营系统等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11901441190144119,
      0.15136558078315235,
      0.9065550906555091,
      0.2033563672260612
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_1",
    "text": "2.沙尘暴现象",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11715481171548117,
      0.21388614675880224,
      0.26778242677824265,
      0.23692003948667326
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_2",
    "text": "我国典型地区：西北.华北地区 产生的原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15527661552766156,
      0.24481737413622903,
      0.4676894467689447,
      0.2968081605791379
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_3",
    "text": "(1)自然原因：快行冷锋天气影响：气候干旱.降水少：春季大风天数多.地表循 被稀少等",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11343561134356113,
      0.3073379401118789,
      0.9446768944676894,
      0.3599868377755841
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_4",
    "text": "(2)人为原因：过度放牧：过度樵采：过度开垦 治理措施：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16364481636448164,
      0.36920039486673245,
      0.6387726638772664,
      0.42250740375123397
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_5",
    "text": "制定草场保护的法律、法规，加强管理：控制载畜量：营造“三北防护林建 设：退耕还林、还牧；建设人工草场；推广轮牧；禁止采伐发莱等",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11343561134356113,
      0.43237907206317866,
      0.9465364946536494,
      0.4876604146100691
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_6",
    "text": "3.地震",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11715481171548117,
      0.5264889766370516,
      0.200836820083682,
      0.5475485357025337
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_7",
    "text": "我国典型地区：东部沿海：西南.西北地区 形成原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15806601580660157,
      0.5567620927936822,
      0.5904230590423059,
      0.6094109904573873
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_8",
    "text": "位于亚欧板块和太平洋板块，印度洋板块的交界处，地壳活动剧烈。 造成重大人员和财产损失的原因可能有：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15527661552766156,
      0.6186245475485357,
      0.8572756857275686,
      0.6752221125370188
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_9",
    "text": "震级大，破坏性大：震中附近城市分而多，人口集中：浅源地震发生的时间可 能在夜间：诱发其他灾害争",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1199442119944212,
      0.6811451135241856,
      0.9344490934449093,
      0.736426456071076
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_10",
    "text": "减轻灾害的措施：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17387261738726173,
      0.7436656794998354,
      0.3719200371920037,
      0.7660414610069102
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102_11",
    "text": "积报开展防灾、减灾的宣传教育，提高公众的环保和减灾意识：建立灾害 监测预报体系：加强地质灾害的管理.建立健全减灾工作的政策法规体系；提 高建筑物的抗震强度；植树造林，建立防护林体系：加强国际合作等.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12087401208740121,
      0.773938795656466,
      0.9465364946536494,
      0.8608094768015795
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_102",
    "order": 12
  },
